<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Redstone Compendium</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&family=VT323:wght@400&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --red: #cc2200;
    --red-bright: #ff3300;
    --red-glow: #ff4422;
    --red-dim: #661100;
    --stone: #7a7a7a;
    --stone-dark: #2a2a2a;
    --stone-mid: #3d3d3d;
    --stone-light: #555555;
    --bg: #111111;
    --text: #e8e0d0;
    --text-dim: #999;
    --gold: #ffaa00;
    --easy: #44cc44;
    --medium: #ffaa00;
    --hard: #ff6600;
    --extreme: #cc2200;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: default;
  }

  /* Pixel grid background */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(204,34,0,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(204,34,0,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 32px 32px;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  /* ===== HEADER ===== */
  .header {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px 40px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--red-dim);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a0800 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .header::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--red-bright), var(--red-glow), var(--red-bright), transparent);
    animation: scanline 3s linear infinite;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--red-glow);
  }

  @keyframes scanline {
    0% { opacity: 0.5; } 50% { opacity: 1; } 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
  }

  .dust-particles {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .particle {
    position: absolute;
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--red-glow);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: float var(--dur) var(--delay) ease-in-out infinite;
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--red-glow);
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
    20% { opacity: 0.8; }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-120px) translateX(var(--drift)); }
  }

  .header-icon {
    font-size: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px var(--red-glow));
    animation: pulse-icon 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-icon {
    0%, 100% { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px var(--red-glow)); }
    50% { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px var(--red-glow)) drop-shadow(0 0 60px var(--red)); }
  }

  .title {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 4vw, 32px);
    color: var(--red-bright);
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--red-glow), 3px 3px 0 var(--red-dim);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--stone-light);
    margin-top: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
  }

  /* ===== NAV SLIDER ===== */
  .nav-rail {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(17,17,17,0.97);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--red-dim);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .nav-inner {
    display: flex;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    gap: 0;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .nav-inner::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

  .nav-btn {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding: 14px 22px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .nav-btn::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--red-bright);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--red-glow);
  }

  .nav-btn:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .nav-btn.active { color: var(--red-bright); }
  .nav-btn.active::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

  .nav-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 0;
    background: currentColor;
    margin-right: 8px;
    vertical-align: middle;
    position: relative;
    top: -1px;
  }

  /* ===== PROGRESS SLIDER ===== */
  .progress-bar {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--red-bright);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--red-glow);
    transition: width 0.1s;
    z-index: 200;
  }

  /* ===== SECTIONS ===== */
  .section {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 24px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--stone-mid);
    margin: 0 24px;
  }

  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: clamp(10px, 2vw, 14px);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border: 1px solid;
    border-radius: 0;
  }

  .tag-easy { color: var(--easy); border-color: var(--easy); background: rgba(68,204,68,0.1); }
  .tag-medium { color: var(--medium); border-color: var(--medium); background: rgba(255,170,0,0.1); }
  .tag-hard { color: var(--hard); border-color: var(--hard); background: rgba(255,102,0,0.1); }
  .tag-extreme { color: var(--extreme); border-color: var(--extreme); background: rgba(204,34,0,0.15); }
  .tag-tutorial { color: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold); background: rgba(255,170,0,0.1); }

  .label-easy { color: var(--easy); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--easy); }
  .label-medium { color: var(--medium); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--medium); }
  .label-hard { color: var(--hard); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--hard); }
  .label-extreme { color: var(--extreme); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--extreme); }
  .label-tutorial { color: var(--gold); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--gold); }

  /* ===== CARDS GRID ===== */
  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--stone-dark);
    border: 1px solid var(--stone-mid);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--accent);
  }

  .card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top left, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .card:hover::before {
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px var(--accent);
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .card-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .card-steps {
    margin-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--stone-light);
    padding-top: 16px;
  }

  .card-steps-title {
    font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .card-steps ol {
    padding-left: 18px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .card-steps ol li::marker {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .card-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px; right: 16px;
    font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .difficulty-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }

  .bar-pip {
    height: 4px;
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--stone-light);
    border-radius: 0;
  }

  .bar-pip.lit {
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--accent);
  }

  /* Easy */
  .card[data-diff="easy"] { --accent: var(--easy); }
  .card[data-diff="medium"] { --accent: var(--medium); }
  .card[data-diff="hard"] { --accent: var(--hard); }
  .card[data-diff="extreme"] { --accent: var(--extreme); }
  .card[data-diff="tutorial"] { --accent: var(--gold); }

  /* ===== TUTORIAL CARDS ===== */
  .tutorial-card {
    background: var(--stone-dark);
    border: 1px solid var(--stone-mid);
    padding: 28px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
    --accent: var(--gold);
  }

  .tutorial-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--gold);
  }

  .tutorial-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .tutorial-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .tutorial-tag-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .t-tag {
    font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--stone-light);
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  .t-tag.featured {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .step-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .step-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 8px;
    color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(255,170,0,0.1);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 4px 7px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .step-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ===== INTRO SECTION ===== */
  .intro-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .intro-block {
    border: 1px solid var(--stone-mid);
    padding: 20px;
    background: rgba(42,42,42,0.5);
    position: relative;
  }

  .intro-block-icon {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .intro-block-title {
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--red-bright);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .intro-block p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ===== REDSTONE SCHEMATIC (ASCII Art Style) ===== */
  .schematic {
    background: #0a0a0a;
    border: 1px solid var(--stone-mid);
    padding: 16px;
    font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--red-bright);
    margin-top: 16px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    white-space: pre;
    line-height: 1.4;
    text-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--red-glow);
  }

  /* ===== SCROLL TO TOP ===== */
  .scroll-top {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 30px;
    right: 30px;
    z-index: 100;
    background: var(--stone-dark);
    border: 1px solid var(--red-dim);
    color: var(--red-bright);
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 18px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .scroll-top.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: all;
  }

  .scroll-top:hover {
    background: var(--red-dim);
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px var(--red-glow);
  }

  /* ===== COMPONENTS DESC ===== */
  .comp-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .comp-table th {
    text-align: left;
    font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--red-bright);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--red-dim);
    background: rgba(204,34,0,0.06);
  }

  .comp-table td {
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone-mid);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .comp-table tr:hover td {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .comp-table td:first-child {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  em-r { color: var(--red-bright); font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; }
  em-g { color: var(--easy); font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; }
  em-y { color: var(--medium); font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="progress-bar" id="progress"></div>

<!-- Header -->
<div class="header">
  <div class="dust-particles" id="particles"></div>
  <span class="header-icon">🔴</span>
  <h1 class="title">Redstone<br>Compendium</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">◆ THE ADVANCED ENGINEER'S GUIDE ◆</p>
</div>

<!-- Navigation -->
<nav class="nav-rail">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <button class="nav-btn active" onclick="scrollTo('intro')"><span class="nav-pill"></span>Basics</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="scrollTo('easy')"><span class="nav-pill" style="color:var(--easy)"></span>Easy</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="scrollTo('medium')"><span class="nav-pill" style="color:var(--medium)"></span>Medium</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="scrollTo('hard')"><span class="nav-pill" style="color:var(--hard)"></span>Hard</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="scrollTo('extreme')"><span class="nav-pill" style="color:var(--extreme)"></span>Extreme</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="scrollTo('tutorials')"><span class="nav-pill" style="color:var(--gold)"></span>Tutorials</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- INTRO -->
<section class="section" id="intro">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div>
      <span class="section-tag tag-tutorial">01 — FOUNDATIONS</span>
      <h2 class="section-label" style="color:var(--text); margin-top:10px;">Redstone Basics</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p style="color:var(--text-dim); font-size:17px; max-width:700px; line-height:1.8;">
    Redstone is Minecraft's electrical system — a complex web of signals, logic gates, and mechanical contraptions. Master these fundamentals before advancing to complex circuits.
  </p>

  <table class="comp-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Component</th>
        <th>Function</th>
        <th>Signal Strength</th>
        <th>Notes</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>🔴 Redstone Dust</td><td>Carries signal across surfaces</td><td>Decreases by 1/block (max 15)</td><td>Place repeaters every 15 blocks</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🔁 Repeater</td><td>Extends signal, adds delay</td><td>Resets to 15</td><td>Can be locked by adjacent repeater</td></tr>
      <tr><td>⚡ Comparator</td><td>Compares/subtracts signals</td><td>Variable</td><td>Key for advanced logic</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🕹️ Lever</td><td>Continuous ON/OFF power source</td><td>15</td><td>Toggles — stays in position</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🔘 Button</td><td>Momentary pulse source</td><td>15 (brief)</td><td>Stone = 1 tick, Wood = 1.5 ticks</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🔡 Piston</td><td>Pushes blocks on power</td><td>—</td><td>Max 12-block push</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🏋️ Sticky Piston</td><td>Pushes and pulls blocks</td><td>—</td><td>Cannot pull slime/honey blocks</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🔦 Redstone Torch</td><td>Always-on power source / NOT gate</td><td>15 (dim=0)</td><td>Inverts signal above/beside</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🔔 Observer</td><td>Detects block state changes</td><td>15 (1 tick pulse)</td><td>Crucial for farms and detectors</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🧲 Dropper/Dispenser</td><td>Ejects items on pulse</td><td>—</td><td>Dropper doesn't activate items</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="intro-grid">
    <div class="intro-block">
      <div class="intro-block-icon">⏱️</div>
      <div class="intro-block-title">Tick System</div>
      <p>1 game tick = 0.05 seconds. Redstone ticks are <em-r>2 game ticks</em-r> (0.1s). Repeaters add 1–4 RT delay.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-block">
      <div class="intro-block-icon">🔁</div>
      <div class="intro-block-title">Signal Power</div>
      <p>Signal starts at 15, drops by 1 per block. At 0 it dies. Use repeaters to <em-r>boost back to 15</em-r>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-block">
      <div class="intro-block-icon">⬆️</div>
      <div class="intro-block-title">Vertical Signals</div>
      <p>Use repeaters going upward or dust on <em-r>staircase blocks</em-r>. Comparators work similarly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-block">
      <div class="intro-block-icon">🧱</div>
      <div class="intro-block-title">Powered Blocks</div>
      <p>Solid opaque blocks can be <em-r>powered</em-r> (strongly or weakly). This distinction matters for piston timing.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="section-divider">

<!-- EASY -->
<section class="section" id="easy">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div>
      <span class="section-tag tag-easy">02 — DIFFICULTY</span>
      <h2 class="section-label label-easy" style="margin-top:10px;">Easy Circuits</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p style="color:var(--text-dim); font-size:17px; max-width:700px; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:40px;">
    Perfect for beginners. These circuits use a handful of components and teach the fundamentals of signal flow and basic logic.
  </p>
  <div class="cards">

    <div class="card" data-diff="easy">
      <span class="card-badge">EASY — 1/5</span>
      <span class="card-icon">💡</span>
      <div class="card-title">Simple Light Switch</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Connect a lever to a lamp via redstone dust. The foundation of every redstone circuit.</div>
      <div class="difficulty-bar">
        <div class="bar-pip lit"></div><div class="bar-pip"></div><div class="bar-pip"></div><div class="bar-pip"></div><div class="bar-pip"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-steps">
        <div class="card-steps-title">// STEPS</div>
        <ol>
          <li>Place a redstone lamp on the ground</li>
          <li>Run redstone dust from the lamp</li>
          <li>Place a lever at the end of the dust trail</li>
          <li>Toggle lever to power the lamp</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" data-diff="easy">
      <span class="card-badge">EASY — 2/5</span>
      <span class="card-icon">🚪</span>
      <div class="card-title">Basic Door Trigger</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Use pressure plates or buttons to open iron doors automatically when approached.</div>
      <div class="difficulty-bar">
        <div class="bar-pip lit"></div><div class="bar-pip lit"></div><div class="bar-pip"></div><div class="bar-pip"></div><div class="bar-pip"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-steps">
        <div class="card-steps-title">// STEPS</div>
        <ol>
          <li>Place an iron door in a doorway</li>
          <li>Lay pressure plates on both sides</li>
          <li>Connect with redstone if plates are far from door</li>
          <li>Walk over plate to open door automatically</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" data-diff="easy">
      <span class="card-badge">EASY — 3/5</span>
      <span class="card-icon">🔔</span>
      <div class="card-title">NOT Gate (Inverter)</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Using a redstone torch to flip signal state — when input is ON, output is OFF.</div>
      <div class="difficulty-bar">
        <div class="bar-pip lit"></div><div class="bar-pip lit"></div><div class="bar-pip"></div><div class="bar-pip"></div><div class="bar-pip"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-steps">
